{"tid":2316021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[保持熱度] 知唔知聽日係咩日子？","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T15:54:39.000Z","uid":251732,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"536e737b98281966cb18b13e6ea6264b34973bef","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">聽日係周梓樂手足被死亡嘅第13個月， 經歷咗咁耐嘅得同苦難同壓迫 ，大家都仲係面對恐懼之中， 國際戰線亦都因為拜登當選同武肺而處於困局之下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 唔好對咁嘅困局習慣呀 ， 由始至終香港社會已經畀魔鬼顛倒是非黑白， 無論係政治壓迫定係疫情滅絕，目的就係要將我哋呢一個群體徹底消滅 ！<br />\n<br />\n你若放棄 誰衛我城？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0a07425c704259ba34d27e92f28dfe70c109efe9","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">我們永不忘記 我們永不原諒<br />\n我們必定反抗 我們必定報仇<br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n剿滅匪類 刻不容緩<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n香港人 建國<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e016677aeafb302afaa3782997a7383524a9459a","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:18:44.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"792e8f7b579c363134d4cf1e388ae5ad723f6fff","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"a9032f3c1368996487533085904c8644bb003292","tid":2316021,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cffb661ede2a656a23285bdb3b65d21daf6cfa9","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"2bcc3a1f31a28b44ef88cf91bf5e89ed62ab8501","tid":2316021,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9032f3c1368996487533085904c8644bb003292","tid":2316021,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT